 ploads/event/ICE%20OUT_20260419203414005432.png
DESCRIPTION:**Come and join this statewide action at the Allen County Cour
 thouse.** Planned by The **Indiana Organizing Project** across the state\,
  and locally by **Plymouth Church Fort Wayne** and **Indivisible Northeast
  Indiana** taking action to object to ICE detainment at the Miami Correcti
 onal Facility. **Over 70% of ICE detainees have never been convicted of a 
 crime.** **ICE detainees at Miami Correctional Facility report medical neg
 lect.** **Two ICE detainees have died at Miami Correctional Facility 
LOCATION:Allen County Court Administration\, 715 S Calhoun St\, Fort Wayne
 \, IN\, 46802
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblenortheastindiana/event/941852/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
