BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:ACLU-IN Volunteer Social
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260507T143000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260507T163000
UID:3a37cfad16eb33210efb66aedb7c8029@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/volsocial1_20260317202827648089.png
DESCRIPTION:Join us in Indianapolis for a special ACLU of Indiana Voluntee
 r Social! Whether you're fired up about protecting civil liberties\, ready
  to stand up for LGBTQ+ rights\, or just curious about how to get involved
  — we want to meet you. Learn how you can get involved and stay engaged.
  Dinner and N/A drinks provided! Please register to see the event details.
LOCATION:Indianapolis\, IN
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/acluin/event/896878/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Empty Chair Town Hall
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260506T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260506T170000
UID:52f402f6d22bf006ab36605d62c1a846@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Young%20Empty%20Chair%20Town%20Hall%20May%202026%20mobilize%2
 03_20260417125100689545.png
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a Todd Young "Empty Chair" Town Hall. Altho
 ugh Todd Young is unable to join\, we'll still make sure he hears from his
  constituents. Come and tell Young ... No billions for war No billions for
  ICE No billions for billionaires and we'll make sure your message gets to
  his office. We'll deliver a video of the public comments and ask everyone
  to flood his office with postcards.
LOCATION:Broadway United Methodist Church\, 609 E 29th St\, Indianapolis\,
  IN\, 46205
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblecentralindiana/event/937011/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
